name: Labrynth Barrage
desc: When you activate a Set Normal Trap Card, except "Labrynth Barrage": This card's effect becomes that Normal Trap Card's effect when that card is activated, also your opponent takes no damage from your card effects until the end of their next turn after this card resolves.
